The paper deals with quality estimation for automatic subject indexing, which is a task related to information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a deep learning architecture, which involves regression and multi-layered neural networks, indicating a connection to machine learning (ML) and deep learning (DL). Hence, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.DL are also likely sub-categories.
